milestones.description: Dave Houghton has become the top scorer for ZIM in ODIs with 318 runs, going past Kevin Curran's 212
Dave Houghton has scored 3 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for ZIM breaking Kevin Curran's record
Dave Houghton has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (88) in an innings in ODIs for ZIM, going past Dave Houghton's 42
Dave Houghton's 142 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for ZIM), surpassing Dave Houghton's 84
Dave Houghton has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (6) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Dave Houghton's 1
Dave Houghton and Andy Pycroft's 51-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 31 between Jack Heron and Andy Pycroft
Dave Houghton and Iain Butchart's 117-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 34 between Fletcher and Peckover
Robin Brown has broken the record for most catches (4) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Andy Pycroft's 3
Iain Butchart has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (7) for ZIM, going past Kevin Curran
Dave Houghton and Iain Butchart's 117-run partnership is the highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 68 between Bevan Congdon and Lance Cairns
Dave Houghton and Iain Butchart's 117-run partnership is ZIM's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 103 between Dave Houghton and Kevin Curran
